$ Examples for Visual Basic for Application accessing the Windows API: GetTempPath

The Windows API function `GetTempPath` returns the name of the temporary directory.

The following example needs the VBA declarations of the Windows API which can be found
→ development/languages/VBA/Win-API[here].

gh|WinAPI-4-VBA|/examples/GetTempPath.bas||


